description:
The story of the Good Samaritan is still used today as an analogy, motivation and inspiration across societies, cultures, and faiths. It raises the important question as to who is our neighbour? Who should we help? Who should we look out for? As we live in a world full of inequities, division and turmoil we need to ask ourselves, who is our neighbour?
